flowchart TD
    Start([Cliente invoca servicio]) --> CheckProtocol{Protocolo?}
    
    CheckProtocol -->|SOAP| ProxySOAP[RollbackTaxesBulletinSoapPS<br/>Endpoint: /honduras/transfer/soap/rollbackTaxesBulletin/v1]
    CheckProtocol -->|REST| ProxyREST[RollbackTaxesBulletinRestPS<br/>Endpoint: /honduras/transfer/rest/rollbackTaxesBulletin/v1]
    
    ProxySOAP --> ValidateSecurity[Validar Seguridad OWSM<br/>Policy: http_basic_auth_over_ssl_service_policy]
    ProxyREST --> ValidateSecurity
    
    ValidateSecurity --> ValidateSchema[Validar Esquema XML/JSON<br/>Schema: RollbackTaxesBulletinTypes.xsd]
    
    ValidateSchema -->|Válido| InvokePipeline[Invocar Pipeline<br/>RollbackTaxesBulletinPP]
    ValidateSchema -->|Inválido| ErrorSchema[Error de Validación]
    
    ErrorSchema --> ErrorHandler
    
    InvokePipeline --> TemplateStart[Template: TransferHondurasFicohsaTemplate]
    
    TemplateStart --> StageAssignment[StageAssigment<br/>Asignar Variables de Contexto]
    
    StageAssignment --> AssignVars[Variables:<br/>service='Transfer/RollbackTaxesBulletin'<br/>version='v1'<br/>key='TransactionId'<br/>value=TransactionId<br/>method='SOAP'<br/>operationTargetSystem='Reversionpagorecaudorefdbcta'<br/>targetSystem='T24'<br/>security='Y'<br/>user=ApplicationId]
    
    AssignVars --> StageSecurity[StageSecurity<br/>Extracción de Credenciales]
    
    StageSecurity --> CreateUserXML[Crear userLoginElement<br/>con ApplicationId]
    
    CreateUserXML --> ExtractCred[Invocar ExtractCredentials.xqy]
    
    ExtractCred --> LDAPLookup[LDAP Lookup<br/>Path: SB_Security/Common/{ApplicationId}]
    
    LDAPLookup -->|Encontrado| GetCredentials[Obtener username y password]
    LDAPLookup -->|No encontrado| Failover[Failover: usar ApplicationId<br/>como username y password]
    
    GetCredentials --> StoreCredentials[Almacenar en responseUserLogin]
    Failover --> StoreCredentials
    
    StoreCredentials --> StageTransformRequest[StageTransformRequest<br/>Transformar Request Regional a T24]
    
    StageTransformRequest --> InvokeTransformIn[Invocar RollbackTaxesBulletinToT24.xqy]
    
    InvokeTransformIn --> MapFields[Mapeo de Campos:<br/>TransactionId → transactionId<br/>username → userName<br/>password → password<br/>company → '' vacío]
    
    MapFields --> StoreRequestService[Almacenar en requestService]
    
    StoreRequestService --> StageLoggingInput[StageLoggingInput<br/>Logging de Request]
    
    StageLoggingInput --> CheckSecurity{security = 'Y'?}
    
    CheckSecurity -->|Sí| HideRequest[Ocultar requestServiceOri<br/>por seguridad]
    CheckSecurity -->|No| KeepRequest[Mantener requestServiceOri]
    
    HideRequest --> LogRequest[Invocar LoggingRegionalRestBS<br/>Registrar REQUEST]
    KeepRequest --> LogRequest
    
    LogRequest --> StageInvokeCoreBanking[StageInvokeCoreBanking<br/>Invocar T24]
    
    StageInvokeCoreBanking --> WSCallout[wsCallout a ReversarTransaccionSoapT24BS<br/>URL: http://172.23.13.19:7003/RollbackTaxesBulletin/services<br/>Operation: rollbackTaxesBulletin<br/>Timeout: 0<br/>Retry: 0]
    
    WSCallout -->|Éxito| T24Response[Recibir responseService de T24]
    WSCallout -->|Error Conexión| ErrorHandler[Error Handler Pipeline]
    
    T24Response --> ExtractStatus[Extraer de responseService:<br/>statusService = successIndicator<br/>codeErrorService = successIndicator<br/>messageErrorService = messages]
    
    ExtractStatus --> StageLoggingOutput[StageLoggingOutput<br/>Logging de Response]
    
    StageLoggingOutput --> LogResponse[Invocar LoggingRegionalRestBS<br/>Registrar RESPONSE]
    
    LogResponse --> StageTargetSystemToRegional[StageTargetSystemToRegional<br/>Transformar Response T24 a Regional]
    
    StageTargetSystemToRegional --> CheckSuccess{codeErrorService<br/>= 'Success'?}
    
    CheckSuccess -->|Sí| InvokeTransformOut[Invocar T24ToRollbackTaxesBulletin.xqy]
    CheckSuccess -->|No| BuildErrorRequest[Construir requestError<br/>con ServicesToError.xqy]
    
    InvokeTransformOut --> MapSuccessResponse[Mapeo Respuesta Exitosa:<br/>Status = successIndicator<br/>ValueDate = substring current-dateTime 0,11<br/>DateTime = substring current-dateTime 0,20<br/>GlobalId = globalId del request]
    
    MapSuccessResponse --> ReplaceBodySuccess[Reemplazar body con<br/>rollbackTaxesBullletinResponse]
    
    ReplaceBodySuccess --> ReturnSuccess[Retornar Respuesta Exitosa]
    
    BuildErrorRequest --> InvokeErrorMapper[Invocar GetCustomErrorByStackTraceRegionalRestBS<br/>Mapear error T24 a regional]
    
    InvokeErrorMapper --> ReceiveErrorMapping[Recibir responseError:<br/>code, error, description, shortDescription]
    
    ReceiveErrorMapping --> InvokeTransformError[Invocar ErrorToRollbackTaxesBulletin.xqy]
    
    InvokeTransformError --> MapErrorResponse[Mapeo Respuesta Error:<br/>StatusInfo/Status = status<br/>StatusInfo/TransactionId = ''<br/>ErrorInfo/Code = responseError/code<br/>ErrorInfo/Error = responseError/error<br/>ErrorInfo/Description = responseError/description<br/>ErrorInfo/Details/SystemId = 'T24'<br/>ErrorInfo/Details/Messages = messageError]
    
    MapErrorResponse --> ReplaceBodyError[Reemplazar body con<br/>rollbackTaxesBullletinResponse con error]
    
    ReplaceBodyError --> ReturnError[Retornar Respuesta con Error]
    
    ReturnSuccess --> End([Fin])
    ReturnError --> End
    
    ErrorHandler --> StageIT[StageIT<br/>Report error en logs]
    
    StageIT --> StageMappingErrors[StageMappingErrors<br/>Mapear errores de pipeline]
    
    StageMappingErrors --> BuildPipelineError[Construir requestError<br/>systemApplication='Vision+'<br/>errorCode=$fault/errorCode<br/>errorMessage=$fault/reason]
    
    BuildPipelineError --> InvokeErrorMapperPipeline[Invocar GetCustomErrorByStackTraceRegionalRestBS]
    
    InvokeErrorMapperPipeline --> ErrorToRespuesta[ErrorToRespuesta<br/>Invocar ErrorToRollbackTaxesBulletin.xqy]
    
    ErrorToRespuesta --> MapPipelineError[Mapeo Error Pipeline:<br/>codeError=$fault/errorCode<br/>messageError=$fault/reason<br/>targetSystem='T24'<br/>status='Error']
    
    MapPipelineError --> StageLoggingOutputError[StageLoggingOutputError<br/>Logging de Error]
    
    StageLoggingOutputError --> LogError[Invocar LoggingRegionalRestBS<br/>Registrar ERROR con errorDetails]
    
    LogError --> StageRespuesta[StageRespuesta<br/>Reply con error]
    
    StageRespuesta --> End
    
